## Additional Terms for BricsCAD V25 Plugin Development

This Enhanced Construction Takeoff plugin is designed specifically for BricsCAD V25 
and requires the BRX SDK for compilation and operation.

### BricsCAD SDK Requirements:
- BricsCAD V25 Developer License required for commercial use
- BRX SDK components are proprietary to Bricsys NV
- Plugin must comply with BricsCAD licensing terms

### Flexible Architecture Notice:
This software implements a completely flexible color assignment system with 
NO FIXED COLORS - all material assignments are user-defined.

### Commercial Use:
This plugin is intended for professional construction takeoff applications.
Commercial deployment requires appropriate BricsCAD licensing.